{"tid":2261832,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［使唔使餵埋畀你食］你哋唔係老馮要幫你","createTime":"2020-10-28T15:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T15:48:28.000Z","uid":175623,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"01b99f0f7fc7fa890f3701459ecdee5e133016a5","tid":2261832,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"你若放棄 誰衛我城？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d仆街叫人乜撚都唔好做 又笑人哋網上集會叫做咗嘢<br />\n<br />\n唔通你日日坐喺屋企咩都唔做 人哋就會救你？國際線就會幫你？不如煮埋飯餵埋你食啦<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月直到今時今日 國際線既手足仲係到不斷努力冇放棄過<br />\n<br />\n攬炒既目的 唔係攬炒自己同路人 其實仲有好多唔犯法既嘢可以做<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街唔好再散播絕望啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5f5abec654eb5e077e2bbb9bc524611497b763","tid":2261832,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:39:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81f12011c708cad9eac4a12f73e8b55bc4176629","tid":2261832,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:48:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}